reviewText:
These two are some of the better British comedians, but the shows in this set are some what repetitive.
None the less, they are still fantastic and still make me laugh, and the special guests are some of the best also.
Eric and Ernie were the very best. This collection only covers the BBC years but contains a vast amount of their best material.
How can you beat miranda with morcombe and wise they are so funny they make my ribs ace you have  to get it
